Title: UiPath
Description:
We envision a world with a 🤖 for every person. Dedicated to delivering​ the leading #RPA platform for an #AutomationFirst mindset​.

• Thousands of enterprise customers and government agencies use UiPath's Enterprise RPA platform to rapidly deploy software robots that perfectly execute repetitive processes, boosting business productivity, ensuring compliance and enhancing the customer experience across back-office and front-office operations. 

• Our technology is used by thousands of companies particularly in document management, call center, healthcare, financial, API enablement, data extraction and migration, process automation, application integration and business process outsourcing verticals.

• We encourage the best minds to contribute and create the next leap in RPA. More than 120.000  developers are building upon the free UiPath Community Edition today, we brought UiPath Academy to the world as the first open online training and certification platform dedicated to RPA users.
